n_sample = 500
p1 <- data %>% sample_n(n_sample) %>% 
  filter(!user_statuses_count==0,!retweet_count==0) %>% 
  ggplot() +
  geom_point(mapping = aes(x = user_statuses_count, y =retweet_count)) +
  scale_x_log10() +
  scale_y_log10()

p1

  ggplot() +

  scale_x_log10() +
  scale_y_log10()
